#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Enable a wireless device\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"啟用無綿網路設備\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "When Tails starts, Wi-Fi, WWAN, and WiMAX devices are enabled."
msgstr " Tails 啟動後， Wi-Fi、 WWAN 與 WiMAX 設備也會跟著啟動。"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"bug\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"bug\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>BlueTooth is enabled by default but Tails lacks the GNOME utilities\n"
"to actually use it.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>藍牙設備預設為啟動，但 Tails 欠缺 GNOME 工具\n"
"能實際來使用它。</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"But all other kinds of wireless devices such as GPS and FM devices are "
"disabled by default. If you want to use such a device, you need to enable it "
"first."
msgstr ""
"但其它的無線設備如 GPS 和 FM 則不會啟動，如果要使用這類設備，請先自行打開它"
"們。"

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Enable a wireless device\n"
msgstr "開啟無線設備\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "This technique uses the command line."
msgstr "這個技巧是使用命令列指令。"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"When starting Tails, [[set up an administration password|doc/first_steps/"
"startup_options/administration_password]]."
msgstr ""
"Tails 啟動時， [[設定一個管理員密碼|doc/first_steps/startup_options/"
"administration_password]]."

#. type: Bullet: '2. '
msgid ""
"To find out the index of the wireless device that you want to enable, open a "
"[[root terminal|doc/first_steps/startup_options/"
"administration_password#open_root_terminal]], and execute the following "
"command:"
msgstr ""
"欲找出要啟動的無線設備目錄索引，請利用[[root terminal|doc/first_steps/"
"startup_options/administration_password#open_root_terminal]]，並執行以下指"
"令："

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "       rfkill list\n"
msgstr "       rfkill list\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   For example, the command could return the following:\n"
msgstr "   指令可能會傳回以下的結果：\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"       0: phy0: Wireless LAN\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
"       1: hci0: Bluetooth\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
"       2: gps0: GPS\n"
"               Soft blocked: yes\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
msgstr ""
"   0: phy0: Wireless LAN\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
"       1: hci0: Bluetooth\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
"       2: gps0: GPS\n"
"               Soft blocked: yes\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   The device index is the number that appears at the beginning of the\n"
"   three lines describing each device. In this example, the index of the Bluetooth\n"
"   device is 1, while the index of the GPS device is 2. Yours are\n"
"   probably different.\n"
msgstr ""
"  設備代號是出現在描述每個設備\n"
"  開頭前三行的數字。本例中，藍牙設備的\n"
"  編號是 1，而 GPS 設備的編號是 2。當然每個人\n"
"  的情況可能稍有不同。\n"

#. type: Bullet: '3. '
msgid ""
"To enable the wireless device, execute the following command in the root "
"terminal, replacing `[index]` with the index found at step 2:"
msgstr ""
"啟動無線設備，請在根管理員終端機中執行以下指令，但請記得把 `[index]`替換為在"
"步驟 2 所查出的代號："

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "       rfkill unblock [index]\n"
msgstr "       rfkill unblock [index]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   Here is an example of the command to execute. Yours is probably\n"
"   different:\n"
msgstr ""
"   以下是一些指令執行的例案，每個人的情況 \n"
"   或有不同差異：\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "       rfkill unblock 2\n"
msgstr "       rfkill unblock 2\n"

#. type: Bullet: '4. '
msgid ""
"To verify that the wireless device is enabled, execute the following command "
"in the root terminal again:"
msgstr "檢查無線設備是否已啟動，請在根管理員終端機再次執行以下指令："

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   This output should be very similar to the one of step 2, but\n"
"   the device enabled at step 3 should not be soft\n"
"   blocked anymore.\n"
msgstr ""
"   這個結果應該和步驟 2 之一有點類似，但\n"
"   在步驟 3 啟動的設備應該\n"
"   不會再遭軟封鎖。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"       0: phy0: Wireless LAN\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
"       1: hci0: Bluetooth\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
"       2: gps0: GPS\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
msgstr ""
"       0: phy0: Wireless LAN\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
"       1: hci0: Bluetooth\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"
"       2: gps0: GPS\n"
"               Soft blocked: no\n"
"               Hard blocked: no\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<!--\n"
msgstr "<!--\n"

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Enable Bluetooth\n"
msgstr "啟動藍牙\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Bluetooth is not enabled by default in Tails because it is insecure when "
"trying to protect from a local adversary."
msgstr ""
" Tails 系統並未把藍牙放入預設啟動，因它本身在防備本地區域中的敵手上並不安"
"全。 "

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To use Bluetooth in Tails nonetheless, you have to [[set up an "
"administration password at boot time|doc/first_steps/startup_options/"
"administration_password]] and install the `gnome-bluetooth` package."
msgstr ""
"在 Tails 使用藍牙，必須 [[在開機時設定管理員密碼|doc/first_steps/"
"startup_options/administration_password]]並安裝 `gnome-bluetooth` 套件包。"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "-->\n"
msgstr "-->\n"
